Matt KnutsonPhD CandidateDepartment of Visual StudiesUniversity of California, Irvine











 
















Matt Knutson is a doctoral candidate in UC Irvine’s Program in Visual Studies. His research focuses on media temporality, esports, and the optimization of play. His dissertation is titled “Frame-Perfect: Temporalities in Competitive Gaming.”





































